        #how_it_works
            .how_it_works
                .imgLeft
                    img(src="img/user_diagram.jpg")
                .textRight
                    h1 HOW IT WORKS
                    h3 FogMeister will continuously monitor the humidity in your car in order to detect when the windscreen has fogged up. When it detects this, a notification will be sent to your phone. You then have the option to activate a dehumidifier in the car such that by the time you need to get in, your car will be ready to drive, avoiding any further delays to your journey!
